<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Read-Rite raised to buy.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Read-Rite raised to buy.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Salomon Brothers said it upgraded Read-Rite Corp to buy from hold.</p>
<p>-- said many of its previous concerns regarding Read-Rite's technology transitions and planar technology have been &quot;largely mitigated.&quot;</p>
<p>-- said raised the 1997 earnings estimate to $1.89 a share from $1.26 a share and the 1998 estimate to $3.63 a share from $2.37 a share.</p>
<p>-- Read-Rite gained 2-1/8 to 27-1/8.</p>
